snippet.title: Star Trek Prodigy: Supernova - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready for an epic intergalactic adventure? 💫 Star Trek: Prodigy is getting its first video game ever! 🖖 Set off into space as Dal R'El and Gwyndala in a race against time to save their friends, the Protostar, and a new alien species before a supernova destroys them all. 

#StarTrekProdigySupernova is coming this fall! Don't miss it!
